title: To His Excellency the Lord General Monck, Capt. General of all the armies and forces in England, Soctland, and Ireland, and one of the generals at sea. The humble address of the officers of your excellencies army in the name of themselves and their brethren, as it was presented to his excellency this 2d.day of May, 1660. By us whose names are subscribed.
author: England and Wales. Army.
